# Project Screenshots

This folder contains screenshots related to the **AI-Enabled Student Admission System**, a Salesforce-based intelligent admission management solution.

The screenshots demonstrate the Salesforce application structure, custom objects, automation, Agentforce AI configuration, reports, dashboards, and security setup used in the project.

## Screenshots Included

### 1. Salesforce Setup Home

Shows the Salesforce Setup interface used to configure the project environment.

### 2. Student Admission Lightning App

Displays the custom **AI-Enabled Student Admission System** Lightning application and its admission management navigation.

### 3. Program Object Manager

Shows the custom Program object used to manage academic programs, departments, eligibility criteria, and admission capacity.

### 4. Document Verification Object

Displays the custom Document Verification object used to track applicant document verification and verification status.

### 5. AI Feedback Object

Shows the AI Feedback object used to capture admission officer feedback on AI-generated admission guidance.

### 6. Admission Application Record

Displays a sample admission application containing applicant information, academic percentage, application status, completeness, missing documents, and AI Admission Guidance.

### 7. Academic Percentage Validation Rule

Shows the validation rule used to prevent an admission application from being submitted without the applicant's academic percentage.

### 8. Admission Application Evaluation Flow

Displays the Salesforce record-triggered flow designed to evaluate application completeness, program eligibility, and document status.

### 9. Admission Status Email Template

Shows the email template used to notify applicants when their admission application status changes.

### 10. Agentforce AI Admission Assistant

Displays the Agentforce-based Student Admission Assistant used to generate AI-assisted admission guidance.

### 11. Admission Reports Folder

Shows the admission reports created for application status, program demand, and application review performance.

### 12. Admission Management Dashboard

Displays the dashboard used to monitor application status, applications by program, and admission review performance.

### 13. Admission Officer Profile

Shows the Salesforce profile configuration for the Admission Officer role.

### 14. Admission Manager Profile

Displays the Salesforce profile configuration for the Admission Manager role.

### 15. Permission Sets

Shows the **AI Admission Feature Access** and **Admission Report Access** permission sets used to provide feature-specific access.

